Last week, I was feeling early depression symptoms after a professional set-back. I called up my friend Nuno.
&ldquo;Do you want me to listen to your ramblings, or do you want to solve the problem?&rdquo;
30 minutes later, we turned to solving the problem. &ldquo;You must stop self-pitying.&rdquo;
After the call, I gave myself evidence that I was the kind of person who was on the path to achieving my goals.
